1 appo int a mutually agreed-upon third mediator. The three mediators
2 shall agree upon a sales price for the hospital license, if the
3 hospital and the municipality cannot agree without mediation. The
4 hospital license shall be purchased and transferred to the city or
5 county if the city or county is willing to pay the agreed-upon
6 purchase price set forth by the mediators.
7 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
